[[A Yuletide Bonfire]] is lit in [[Seaside Town]] on [[Yuletide]]. Bring some [[marshmallow]]s to [[roasted marshmallow|roast]] and listen to the spooooky stories.
Adventuring with a marshmallow in your inventory turns it into a roasted marshmallow. 
