==Notes==
*When [[Beaten Up]] by these adventures, the effect lasts 4 turns instead of the normal 3.
*You will lose X HP in {{element|Spooky}}, where X = (level*2) + random(level).  This damage is unaffected by any {{element|Spooky|Resistance}}, [[Damage Absorption]], [[Damage Reduction]], or even [[Spookyform]].
*You will gain Y MP, where Y = (level*3) + random(level*3).
*You may not adventure at the bonfire while [[Falling-down drunk]].

